Amazing Discoveries Campmeeting 2023: Onward, Forward, Homeward! 

More than just an annual revival, Amazing Discoveries’ 2023 campmeeting is a once-in-a-lifetime event that you won’t want to miss. What’s special this year? Aside from its being one year closer to Jesus’ return; aside from the fact we’ll be featuring amazing and inspiring speakers like Barbara O’Neill, Randy Skeete, Scott Mayer, and others; at campmeeting this year, we’ll be celebrating 30 years of ministry!
